===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-y|lubricit|y}}

# The quality of being [[lubric]]; [[slipperiness]]; [[instability]]; as, the lubricity of fortune.
# [[smoothness|Smoothness]]; freedom from [[friction]]; also, property which diminishes friction; as, the lubricity of oil.
# [[lasciviousness|Lasciviousness]]; [[propensity]] to [[lewdness]]; [[lechery]]; [[incontinency]]. 

